column5: HAS ANYONE BEEN TO THIS RESORT? THINKING OF GOINGIN JUNE. HOW IS FISHING IN MID-JUNE.THANKS

I have a cabin on Eagle, am retired and spend most of the summers there. I have visited this camp and it looks very good. Also, the owner is a very ok guy. The location of the camp is excellent in that it is close to some of the best musky waters on Eagle. Good Luck
